            horizontal list implementation, displaying it on mobile is simply
            not feasible yet. A gesture-based system could make this
            desktop-optimized tool more accessible on mobile devices.
          </li>
          <li>
            Enhanced filtering options by types, stats, and moves would improve
            the user experience, especially on mobile and tablets where screen
            space is limited and only two columns of Pokemon can be shown at one
            time.
          </li>
          <li>
